    "chinese_traditional": "Taimanin. Gosha Academy student. Up-and-coming talent with promise for a bright future, and a leader of Gosha's \"Public Security Team\".\n\nManipulates \"condensed light\", a type of Lightning Art. Through rigorous training, he developed the ability to gather light energy enough to melt steel. This energy is then stored and used in a special rifle called Baldur, which shines just like day, even when there is no light.\n\nAt first glance, he seems like a pretty girl, but is not a girl. Among the freshmen, some people still mistake him for a girl.",
    "spanish": "Taimanin. Gosha Academy student. Up-and-coming talent with promise for a bright future, and a leader of Gosha's \"Public Security Team\".\n\nManipulates \"condensed light\", a type of Lightning Art. Through rigorous training, he developed the ability to gather light energy enough to melt steel. This energy is then stored and used in a special rifle called Baldur, which shines just like day, even when there is no light.\n\nAt first glance, he seems like a pretty girl, but is not a girl. Among the freshmen, some people still mistake him for a girl."
